<p>Note that this example still uses <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;Resource&gt;</code>, because this component lazily initializes the store for the resource data.</p>

<p>This application has no sidebar, no theming, no <a href="./Authentication.md#useauthenticated-hook">auth control</a> - itâ€™s up to you to add these. From there on, you can customize pretty much anything you want.</p>
